UPDATE projects SET zh = '{"id":"pcb-defect-detection","cover":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/cover.png","category":"大學課程作品","title":"PCB 線路瑕疵偵測：Azure Custom Vision 切塊物件偵測","period":"2026","description":"北大 PCB 瑕疵資料集，挑 6 個板型（01／04／05／06／07／08）× 3 種缺陷（missing_hole 缺孔、mouse_bite 鼠咬、open_circuit 斷路）訓練物件偵測。原圖是 3034×1586 的整板、缺陷框只有約 60px，直接丟 Custom Vision 會被縮到約 512px 而看不見，第一次訓練 mAP 只有 9.6%、Recall 3.1%。改成把大圖切成 600px 小塊再訓練後，mAP 88.2%、Precision 100%。匯出 TensorFlow model.pb，可在 Colab 載入推論。 另把模型包成本機檢測工具，支援批量上傳、缺陷統計與 CSV，並設計「人工回饋→審核→重訓」的 active-learning 迴圈。","tags":["Azure Custom Vision","Object Detection","影像切塊 Tiling","model.pb · TensorFlow","Pascal VOC"],"detail":{"images":[{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/performance.png","caption":"Advanced Training 成果（6 板型）：整體 Precision 100% / Recall 72.3% / mAP 88.2%（threshold 0.5），分缺陷數據見下方"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/pipeline.png","caption":"檢測工具與人工回饋重訓流程：上傳→切塊偵測→批量統計→人工校正→審核核准→只用核准資料重訓"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/dataset.png","caption":"訓練資料：每張大圖以缺陷為中心切成 600px 塊，缺陷框佔比從約 2% 拉到約 12%（綠框為標註）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/validation-zoom.png","caption":"未參與訓練的板型 09–12 驗證（放大）：綠＝標註、紅＝模型預測，三類缺陷定位清楚"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/validation-board.png","caption":"整板偵測：對 held-out 板（型號 09）做切塊推論後把框映射回原圖的完整結果"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_01.jpg","caption":"missing_hole 偵測：板型 09 第 1 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_02.jpg","caption":"missing_hole 偵測：板型 09 第 2 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_03.jpg","caption":"missing_hole 偵測：板型 09 第 3 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_04.jpg","caption":"missing_hole 偵測：板型 09 第 4 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_05.jpg","caption":"missing_hole 偵測：板型 09 第 5 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_06.jpg","caption":"missing_hole 偵測：板型 09 第 6 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-de