＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/09_08.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 09 第 8 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/09_09.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 09 第 9 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/09_10.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 09 第 10 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/10_01.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 10 第 1 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/10_02.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 10 第 2 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/10_03.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 10 第 3 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/10_04.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 10 第 4 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/10_05.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 10 第 5 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/10_06.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 10 第 6 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_01.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 1 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_02.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 2 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_03.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 3 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_04.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 4 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_05.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 5 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_06.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 6 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_07.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 7 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_08.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 8 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_09.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 9 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/11_10.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 11 第 10 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_01.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 1 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_02.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 2 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_03.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 3 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_04.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 4 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_05.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 5 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_06.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 6 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_07.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 7 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_08.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 8 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_09.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 9 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/open-circuit/12_10.jpg","caption":"open_circuit 偵測：板型 12 第 10 張（綠＝標註，紅＝模型預測）"}],"purpose":"作業要求：10 個板型裡至少挑 3 型、至少 3 種缺陷，用物件偵測訓練到 Precision 80% 以上，再對沒看過的板子做檢測，最後匯出 model.pb 能在 Colab 載入。\n\n真正卡住的不是訓練流程，是資料尺度。缺陷框只有約 60 像素，整張板卻是 3034×1586。Custom Vision 會把輸入縮到約 512px，縮完缺陷只剩約 10px，模型根本看不到——第一次照標準流程訓練，mAP 只有 9.6%、Recall 3.1%，等於沒用。","concept":"【第一次失敗：直接上傳整圖】\n把整圖連同 Pascal VOC 標註上傳，用 General (compact) domain 做 Advanced Training。結果 mAP 9.6%、Recall 3.1%——缺陷被縮圖吃掉了。\n\n【解法：影像切塊（tiling）】\n把每張大圖以缺陷框為中心切成 600×600 的小塊，框落在塊內超過 40% 面積才保留，座標重新換算成塊內的 0–1 正規化值。缺陷在塊裡的佔比從約 2% 拉到約 12%，縮到 512px 後仍有約 60px。最終以 6 個板型、3 缺陷共切出 837 塊訓練。\n\n【偵測也要切塊】\n推論時整板一樣會被縮小，所以對 PCB_USED 與驗證板也用同樣方式切塊逐塊偵測，把預測框映射回原圖座標，再用 IoU 0.3 的 NMS 去掉重疊塊造成的重複框。\n\n【匯出與 Colab】\n要能匯出 TensorFlow 一定得用 compact domain。匯出的模型輸出是 YOLO 風格原始張量（節點 model_outputs:0），解碼（anchors + NMS）沿用 Custom Vision 官方的 object_detection.py，沒有自己重寫。Colab 端把官方解碼器、model.pb、labels.txt 一起載入就能推論。","outcome":"【Advanced Training 成果（6 板型，threshold 0.5）】\nPrecision 100%　Recall 72.3%　mAP 88.2%\nmissing_hole　P 100%　R 96.9%　AP 99.6%\nmouse_bite　　P 100%　R 65.1%　AP 82.0%\nopen_circuit　P 100%　R 54.1%　AP 83.0%\n\n【為什麼從 3 板型加到 6 板型】\n一開始只用 3 個板型（01／04／05）訓練，mAP 81.9%，但拿沒看過的板子驗證時，每張大概會多框 1 個——模型把正常、有鑽孔的 via 誤判成缺孔，因為它只看過 3 種板的 via 長相。把訓練板型加到 6 個（多了 06／07／08）後，mAP 升到 88.2%，這類誤報基本消失。\n\n【拿沒訓練過的板型驗證（09–12）】\n訓練用 6 個板型，驗證改用模型完全沒看過的 09、10、11、12 共 106 張缺陷圖：標準答案總共 538 個缺陷，模型輸出 509 個框，現在反而是略為保守（少抓約 5%），不再亂多框。在沒看過的板型上仍穩定抓到缺陷，代表泛化是真的。\n\n【誠實邊界】\nPrecision 100% 一樣是 Custom Vision 交叉驗證的數字，偏樂觀（同一張板切出的塊背景相似會高估）。三類裡 open_circuit 與 mouse_bite 的 recall 偏低（54%、65%），斷路和鼠咬比缺孔細微、形狀也不規則，會漏抓一些；要往下做應該先補這兩類資料。missing_hole 已相當穩（recall 96.9%）。\n\n【後續：檢測工具 + 人工回饋重訓】\n把模型包成一支本機網頁工具：一次拖多張板子批量偵測、依缺孔/鼠咬/斷路分色框出、彙整 NG/OK 與各類數量並匯出 CSV。再加上人工回饋迴圈——檢出結果可標記「多抓（誤報）」與「漏抓（補框）」，經人工逐筆審核核准後，只用核准的校正資料重新訓練，形成 active-learning 閉環。工具為本機 Flask 程式，金鑰留在本機。","tech":[{"group":"影像處理","items":[{"name":"影像切塊 Tiling","desc":"以缺陷框為中心切 600px 塊，框需 ≥40% 面積落在塊內才保留，座標換算回塊內 0–1；缺陷佔比從約 2% 提升到約 12%，是整個專案成敗的關鍵"},{"name":"Pascal VOC 解析","desc":"用 xml.etree.ElementTree 解析 bndbox，把像素座標換算成 Custom Vision 要求的 0–1 正規化座標"}]},{"group":"雲端 AI 服務","items":[{"name":"Azure Custom Vision SDK","desc":"用 Python SDK 走完建專案（compact domain）、批次上傳含框影像、Advanced Training、發布、匯出 TensorFlow 的完整流程；刻意用 Advanced 而非 Quick Train"},{"name":"model.pb 匯出與 Colab 載入","desc":"匯出凍結圖 model.pb（輸入 Placeholder:0、輸出 model_outputs:0），在 Colab 以 tf.compat.v1 載入；YOLO 風格輸出的 anchors／NMS 解碼沿用官方 object_detection.py"}]},{"group":"推論與驗證","items":[{"name":"切塊推論 + NMS","desc":"整板切塊逐塊偵測，預測框映射回原圖，再以 IoU 0.3 的 NMS 去除重疊塊造成的重複框"},{"name":"Held-out 驗證","desc":"用模型沒看過的板型 09–12 共 106 張做泛化測試，疊綠（標註）紅（預測）框輸出；標準答案 538 個缺陷對模型輸出 509 個，直接驗證在新板上的表現而不是只信交叉驗證的數字"}]},{"group":"應用工具","items":[{"name":"批量檢測介面","desc":"Flask 本機網頁，拖曳多張板子批量偵測、分色框出三類缺陷、彙整 NG/OK 與各類數量並匯出 CSV"},{"name":"人工回饋迴圈","desc":"檢出結果可標記多抓(誤報)與漏抓(補框)存成校正資料；經人工審核核准後只用核准資料重訓，形成 active-learning 閉環"}]}],"github":""}}', en = '{"id":"pcb-defect-detection","cover":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/cover.png","category":"University Coursework","title":"PCB Trace Defect Detection: Tiled Object Detection with Azure Custom Vision","period":"2026","description":"Object detection on the Peking University PCB defect dataset, using 6 board types (01/04/05/06/07/08) and 3 defect classes (missing_hole, mouse_bite, open_circuit). The source images are full 3034×1586 boards where each defect box is only ~60px. Custom Vision shrinks input to ~512px, so defects vanished and the first training run reached only 9.6% mAP / 3.1% recall. After slicing each board into 600px tiles, mAP went up to 88.2% and precision to 100%. The TensorFlow model.pb is exported and loads in Colab. The model was also wrapped into a local inspection tool with batch upload, defect statistics and CSV export, plus a human feedback → review → retrain active-learning loop.","tags":["Azure Custom Vision","Object Detection","Image Tiling","model.pb · TensorFlow","Pascal VOC"],"detail":{"images":[{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/performance.png","caption":"Advanced Training result (6 board types): overall Precision 100% / Recall 72.3% / mAP 88.2% (threshold 0.5); per-class numbers below"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/pipeline.png","caption":"Inspection tool & human-feedback retrain loop: upload → tiled detect → batch stats → manual correction → review/approve → retrain on approved data only"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/dataset.png","caption":"Training data: each board is sliced into 600px tiles centered on defects, raising defect-to-tile ratio from ~2% to ~12% (green = ground truth)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/validation-zoom.png","caption":"Held-out boards 09–12 (zoomed): green = ground truth, red = model prediction, across all three defect classes"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/validation-board.png","caption":"Full-board detection: tiled inference on a held-out board (type 09) with boxes mapped back to the original image"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_01.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #1 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_02.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #2 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_03.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #3 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_04.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #4 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_05.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #5 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_06.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #6 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_07.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #7 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_08.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #8 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_09.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #9 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/09_10.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 09, #10 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/10_01.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 10, #1 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/10_02.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 10, #2 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/10_03.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 10, #3 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/10_04.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 10, #4 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/10_05.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 10, #5 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_01.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #1 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_02.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #2 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_03.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #3 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_04.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #4 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_05.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #5 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_06.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #6 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_07.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #7 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_08.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #8 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_09.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #9 (green = ground truth, red = prediction)"},{"src":"/images/pcb-defect-detection/missing-hole/11_10.jpg","caption":"missing_hole detection — board 11, #10 (green = ground truth, red = prediction